{"tid":1797373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（討論)如何杜絕便衣狗？","createTime":"2019-12-25T11:00:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-25T11:30:49.000Z","uid":2076,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"fe3e76df01b47960d842ae19a55679990ad29746","tid":1797373,"uid":2076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T11:00:07.000Z","msg":"啲狗俾你捉到，又唔係真係開佢波<br />\n便衣冇成本，已經令在場人士喺惶恐之中<br />\n<br />\n所以如果要令班狗唔敢岀便衣，<br />\n就要令佢地變得有成本/風險"},{"pid":"a8ac7ed7a24a734331ef06b040b1f22386d270e4","tid":1797373,"uid":2076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T11:00:58.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"pid":"f4cc01ba07bb2428f45cdd8df41dcc8cf5394c25","tid":1797373,"uid":2076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T11:01:12.000Z","msg":"推2"},{"pid":"06c074aced9f179f735a2c1f5a69d3dd6f0decb4","tid":1797373,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T11:01:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"049f2ce93c43c8366a1d309672f679b2362dc0ac","tid":1797373,"uid":226984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T11:02:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44d5ac867484f2505343029aef021e03e1b9969d","tid":1797373,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T11:02:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"462847f0d57ff2a3bb606174980c65e4688aab37","tid":1797373,"uid":197716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T11:04:17.000Z","msg":"推 好難拆"},{"pid":"311ecbd586f657b956bdd26d4cc55ccee6c0a473","tid":1797373,"uid":71428,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T11:07:44.000Z","msg":"唔捉鬼<br />\n捉又唔夠打<br />\n唔轉dress code<br />\n冬天zip 衫都冇用<br />\n<br />\n冇解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e168aae260a466cf8e99a47727b6c320dbc833fe","tid":1797373,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T11:08:28.000Z","msg":"捉到--&gt;打--&gt;1分鐘內其他便衣到--&gt;襲警<br />\n捉到--&gt;屌--&gt;1分鐘內其他便衣到--&gt;鳩拉<br />\n仲要商場周圍都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n令到裝修風險高左好多<br />\n<br />\n如果成班手足(無裝、和理非)<br />\n去藍店門口屌 唔郁手<br />\n屌到佢關門／客走<br />\n再去第二間 不斷loop 咁得唔得？"},{"pid":"e0d2f49a8254da05cc56d3edb49fbb9bf00a413b","tid":1797373,"uid":114781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T11:09:31.000Z","msg":"解決方法同麻包袋一樣。不過張name list長過聖經都未有人做、班曱甴點解要驚你？"},{"pid":"34bff8f25090907b00311d60b4ae82b84267a615","tid":1797373,"uid":263618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T11:10:39.000Z","msg":"popo strategy<br />\n<br />\n1.其實冇部署，忠誠勇毅嘅佢哋係唔怕經濟攬炒<br />\n怕經濟攬炒嘅只係施生陳生嗰啲收成期買晒鋪嘅人<br />\n呢個係上面嘅指令<br />\n佢地只會不斷咁樣irritate你<br />\n每隔一段時間就會irritate你<br />\n目的係想你哋開花，捉晒有膽量行動嘅人<br />\n剩返嗰啲今時今日都冇膽行出嚟嘅，將來23條呀國歌戲出咗之後更加唔會夠膽出聲，所以嗰啲人響上面來講係廢嘅，上面覺得只要捉實夠膽行出黎嘅就代表成功<br />\n<br />\n2. 有人受傷究竟可唔可以喚醒啲人or 輸出革命？遙遠有集中營嘅地方有人自焚有人俾人強姦有人俾人殺，兼且佢哋好齊心，佢哋而家成功咗未？<br />\n<br />\n3. 其實我寫呢句出嚟係想同大家講,和你shop你只要夠多人,去啲鋪頭睇下野,靜靜地已經可以達致你當初想經濟攬炒嘅目的唔需要咁樣正面的diu狗,太揚啦，POPO 嘅接到order 嘅我point 1 已經講咗<br />\n琴日嗰兩個跌落樓嘅大命，戰場上希望大家有個安全聖誕"},{"pid":"29b2f3d1f94d349b815d3e1e92fe2e22350d317b","tid":1797373,"uid":284642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T11:10:42.000Z","msg":"阻阻位，希望抽時間睇下同指教<br />\n<br />\n每一個人既力量都係決定香港人成敗既關鍵<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1797377\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1797377</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cbc6a0bf80e0fe907956402bbad286c8b599efd7","tid":1797373,"uid":97523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T11:11:16.000Z","msg":"其實得兩個方法<br />\n<br />\n一個係唔理佢 當佢地透明<br />\n一係直接開佢波 當藍絲處理"},{"pid":"72e86063666584ed70514671ed502507cb5ada14","tid":1797373,"uid":111153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T11:25:07.000Z","msg":"放火燒or用聖水？千祈唔好做呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"319d4d888dc7a45f41fdb5050d05bc9c7d9b9fef","tid":1797373,"uid":36065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T11:25:38.000Z","msg":"真係開佢波"},{"pid":"91ccc5115cad28619631e725f7ddee925191a16d","tid":1797373,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"311ecbd586f657b956bdd26d4cc55ccee6c0a473","tid":1797373,"uid":71428,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T11:07:44.000Z","msg":"唔捉鬼<br />\n捉又唔夠打<br />\n唔轉dress code<br />\n冬天zip 衫都冇用<br />\n<br />\n冇解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T11:30:49.000Z","msg":"人地就係想你捉，等你自己人內耗<br />\n<br />\n正確方法，學堂主話齋，<br />\n就係不割+佢行一步，你行十步<br />\n例如，假設鬼走去爆立會玻璃，我地就衝埋入去<br />\n但要成功必須有文宣配合<br />\n大家要夠齊心"}]}